<h1 style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 3.2em;line-height: 1.04167;font-weight: 700;text-transform: none;">Pay to legalise documents by post</h1>

<h2 style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1.5em;line-height: 1.04167;font-weight: bold;text-transform: none;">Authorisation for payment taken</h2>

<p style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Thank you for your order from the Foreign & Commonwealth Office. We have taken pre-authorisation for the following:</p>


<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Date: <%= date %></p>
<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Payment Reference: <%= merchantReference %></p>
<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Service: <%= slug %></p>
<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Number of items: <%= dc %></p>
<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Amount: &pound;<%= pa %></p>
<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Card type: <%= paymentMethod %></p>
<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Card number: XXXX XXXX XXXX <%= lastFourDigits %></p>
<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">You have paid &pound;<%= pa %> for <%= documents %> including <%= postage %> postage</p>


<p style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">When we have confirmed we can provide the service we will take the payment and send you a receipt.</p>


<h2 style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1.5em;line-height: 1.04167;font-weight: bold;text-transform: none;">What to do next</h2>

<p style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Send the following items to the Legalisation Office:</p>

<ul>
  <li style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">the documents you want legalised</li>
  <li style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">a signed <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/legalisation-application-form">Legalisation application form</a> (with your payment number added)</li>
  <li style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">a print out of this email or payment confirmation page</li>
  <% if (postage == 'PREPAID'){ %> 
  <li style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">an A4-sized prepaid envelope so your documents can be returned</li> 
  <% } %>
</ul>

<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Legalisation Office</p>
<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Foreign &amp; Commonwealth Office</p>
<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">PO Box 6255</p>
<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Milton Keynes</p>
<p style="text-indent: 25px;font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">MK10 1XX</p>

<p style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">You must post your application and documents - you can't go to the legalisation office in person.</p>

<h2 style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1.5em;line-height: 1.04167;font-weight: bold;text-transform: none;">If you’re abroad or using a courier</h2>
  
<p style="font-family:nta, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:1em; line-height:1.31579; font-weight:50 text-transform:none;">Send your registration to the following address if you’re abroad or using a courier service in the UK:</p>
  
